    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.apng?t=1719995272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=319 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in the captivating world of Little Hero Adventure, where thrilling adventures await.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/406a10d4b18e591bdc9f7155a14bdee2.avif?t=1719995272\" width=632 height=194 /></span><br><br>Traverse levels of varying difficulty, battle cunning enemies, overcome traps and obstacles, discover hidden secrets, and gather berries to aid your village.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/51c00f02f617acc10376dc6ef32522b8.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" width=496 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/51c00f02f617acc10376dc6ef32522b8.webm?t=1719995272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Players will explore diverse biomes: mysterious forests, snowy plains, and deep caves. Each biome presents its own challenges and dangers. <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/2fc64ff01e995d8af9be8ee4cdf62068.avif?t=1719995272\" width=502 height=340 /></span><br><br>In the forest, you’ll encounter traps and hidden secrets, in the snowy biome — battles with formidable yetis, and in the caves — dark corridors and forsaken creatures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/c9f594f0d65a4494529886921ff6ad05.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" width=484 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/c9f594f0d65a4494529886921ff6ad05.webm?t=1719995272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Embark on this exciting journey, collect berries, and bring a ray of hope to your village. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/f47b06eb89ffd3524d67fde9494c6a64.avif?t=1719995272\" width=502 height=262 /></span><br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.apng?t=1719995272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=319 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br>Features:<br><br>Diverse Levels: Navigate through various stages with increasing difficulty.<br>Exciting Battles: Face off against a variety of enemies.<br>Challenging Obstacles: Overcome numerous traps and obstacles that test your skills.<br>Hidden Secrets: Discover hidden areas and secrets to gain rewards.<br>Biome Variety: Explore different biomes.<br>Collect items: Gather cherries to help your village and other items to enhance your adventure.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.apng?t=1719995272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=319 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br>Game Controls and Mechanics<br><br>Movement: Use W, A, S, D keys to move your character.<br>Jump: Press Space to jump.<br>Dash: Hold Shift to dash. Dash can destroy boxes and has a 1.2-second cooldown.<br>Wall Slide: Slide down walls by moving towards them.<br>Attack: Use Left Mouse Button (LMB) to attack and kill monsters.<br><br>You can use a gamepad in the game (not applicable to the menu)<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.apng?t=1719995272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/a3a6d5d38a19a71671e0aeaed503356b.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=319 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br>Little Hero Adventure awaits its hero!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/01f9f19573798ffcd07a8404278044cf.apng?t=1719995272\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049080/extras/01f9f19573798ffcd07a8404278044cf.poster.avif?t=1719995272\" class=\"bb_img\" width=429 height=256 /></picture></span>",
